Ah, Germany! One of the mightiest nations in the world did not become what is today by selling cheap cars or wasting time with political issues. No, Germany is a one-of-a-kind state with a very special breed of inhabitants. Here's what it takes to become a German IN 3 EASY STEPS -- or how they say: Ein richtig deutscher Junge!
